                                    class="bg-[#e3f2fd] text-[#1e88e5] w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#bbdefb] hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-sm border border-[#bbdefb]" title="ç·¨è¼¯">
                                âœï¸
